        <section id="about">
            <div class="about-container">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h3>About Jim</h3>
                    <p>
                        Jim's passion for saving our environment has led him to partner with industry leading 
                        suppliers who not only focus on 'green' technologies, but share in Jim's desire to take steps
                        toward protecting and preserving our resources.
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        His consultative approach has helped many small businesses understand challenging markets,
                        navigate the ups and downs of the green industry and ultimately thrive and grow their business. 
                        Jim has a keen sense of marketing and sales training and he openly shares those skills with his clients.
                        Jim understands that partnering with his clients and being instrumental in their success will only 
                        support the success and growth of The Jim Reck Co.
                    </p>
                    <br />

                    <p>
                        His ability to seek like minded vendors and secure relationships with them has helped build a 
                        company that others look up to. His sourcing and networking abilities, along with his firm grasp of supply
                        chain strategies, has halped the company succeed through rough economic times. Jim is always seeking new 
                        opportunities with companies that share his vision of a greener, more environmentally conscious planet.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

